      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont think they understand. every time i mess up i can see it in their eyes. it just feels like i'm a poison to them. like, if i wasn't here, everything would actually be stable for once. i feel like they'd be better off without the shadow of my failure hanging over them.",
